    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Add the<strong> pepper strips</strong> and cook for 5-7 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> and cook for 5-6 min further</p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
