    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, shred the <strong>chicken</strong> apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Stir the <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> through the peppers – this is your <strong>free range chicken peperonata</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>free range chicken peperonata</strong> with the<strong> cheesy potatoes</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
